contentrichtext.text: '''Category 5''' may refer to: *[[Category 5 (album)|''Category 5'' (album)]], an album from rock band, FireHouse *[[Category 5 cable]], used for carrying data *[[Category 5 computer virus]], as classified by Symantec Corporation *[[Category 5 Records]], a record label *Category 5 Tropical Cyclone, on any of the [[Tropical cyclone scales]] ** Any of several hurricanes listed at [[List of Category 5 Atlantic hurricanes]] or [[List of Category 5 Pacific hurricanes]] *Category 5 Pandemic, on the [[Pandemic Severity Index]] {{disambig}}
